#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
"previous experience with firearms came handy in your now-undeath."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你生前使用火器的經驗在如今的不死之身中派上了用場。"

#. ~ Profession (female Requiem Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
"previous experience with firearms came handy in your now-undeath."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你生前使用火器的經驗在如今的不死之身中派上了用場。"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Thanatos Doll"
msgstr "塔納託斯人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Thanatos Doll"
msgstr "塔納託斯人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Thanatos Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. A tough "
"combatant able to take on the biggest of threats in close combat."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你是一名堅韌的戰士，能夠近身對抗最強大的威脅。"

#. ~ Profession (female Thanatos Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. A tough "
