#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
"graceful dancing has no equals."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你優雅的舞姿無人能及。"

#. ~ Profession (female Romanesque Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
"graceful dancing has no equals."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你優雅的舞姿無人能及。"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Baroque Doll"
msgstr "巴洛克人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Baroque Doll"
msgstr "巴洛克人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Baroque Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
"genetics shifts uncontrollably, but you can utilize it to your advantage"
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你的基因不受控制地變異，但你可以利用這一點來獲得優勢。"

#. ~ Profession (female Baroque Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. Your "
"genetics shifts uncontrollably, but you can utilize it to your advantage"
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你的基因不受控制地變異，但你可以利用這一點來獲得優勢。"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Gothic Doll"
msgstr "哥特人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Gothic Doll"
msgstr "哥特人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Gothic Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You were "
"designed to hunt down the other undead and devour them."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你被設計用來獵殺其他不死生物併吞噬它們。"

#. ~ Profession (female Gothic Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You were "
"designed to hunt down the other undead and devour them."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你被設計用來獵殺其他不死生物併吞噬它們。"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Erudite Doll"
msgstr "博學人偶"

#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Erudite Doll"
msgstr "博學人偶"

#. ~ Profession (male Erudite Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You have "
"the skills to utilize explosives and a proper discipline on its usage."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你擁有使用爆炸物的技能，並對其使用有嚴格的紀律。"

#. ~ Profession (female Erudite Doll) description
#: .\nec_professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"You are a doll, a result of occult reanimation on human corpses. You have "
"the skills to utilize explosives and a proper discipline on its usage."
msgstr "你是一個人偶，是人體屍體經過神秘復活術的產物。你擁有使用爆炸物的技能，並對其使用有嚴格的紀律。"

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's have a long talk.\""
msgstr "\"讓我們好好談談。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Welcome to the story of the miniature garden.\""
msgstr "\"歡迎來到微型花園的故事。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's enjoy the dance of distortion.\""
msgstr "\"讓我們享受扭曲之舞吧。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Did you listen to the play?\""
msgstr "\"你聽了那場戲嗎？\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's have another tea party.\""
msgstr "\"讓我們再開一次茶會吧。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"What is that ringing bell? I wish it would stop.\""
msgstr "\"那是什麼鈴聲？真希望它能停下。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let's make your doll.\""
msgstr "\"讓我們來製作你的人偶吧。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I do not mind failure. You ARE dead after all.\""
msgstr "\"我不介意失敗。畢竟你已經死了。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Dolls are lovely things.\""
msgstr "\"人偶是可愛的東西。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Let the curtain rise and the dead dance.\""
msgstr "\"讓帷幕升起，讓死者起舞。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"... A tin of chicken dumplings? ...\""
msgstr "\"……一罐雞肉餃子？……\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Welcome to the beautiful nightmare.\""
msgstr "\"歡迎來到這美麗的噩夢。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Please humiliate and destroy it.\""
msgstr "\"請羞辱並摧毀它。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Get the ten sided dice.\""
msgstr "\"拿十面骰來。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Now it is time to show you how it is done.\""
msgstr "\"現在是時候向你展示如何做到了。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I am completely beautiful!\""
msgstr "\"我真是美極了！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Oh, those of girls are disgusting people!\""
msgstr "\"哦，那些女孩真是令人作嘔！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I'm not supposed to be complete, just elegant.\""
msgstr "\"我不需要完美，只需優雅。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I am the supreme and solitary necromancer!\""
msgstr "\"我是至高無上且孤獨的死靈法師！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"That is such a crock of...\""
msgstr "\"那真是胡扯……\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"I am the last necromancer you will ever see.\""
msgstr "\"我是你將會見到的最後一位死靈法師。\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"OooooOooooOooo...\""
msgstr "\"嗚哦哦哦哦哦哦……\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"You think you are lucky?\""
msgstr "\"你以為自己很幸運嗎？\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Muha... Muhahaha.... MUHAHAHAHAHAHA!\""
msgstr "\"唔哈……唔哈哈哈……唔哈哈哈哈哈哈！\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"(Sings a song)\""
msgstr "\"（唱起歌來）\""

#: .\nec_speech.json
msgid "\"Haha, a hundred sided dice.\""
msgstr "\"哈哈，一百面骰。\""

#: .\nec_techniques.json
msgid "Wrap Attack"
msgstr "纏繞攻擊"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You wrap up %s"
msgstr "你纏繞住了 %s"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> wraps up %s"
msgstr "<npcname> 纏繞住了 %s"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
msgid "Kung-fu below"
msgstr "下盤功夫"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You attack %s powerfully."
msgstr "你強力地攻擊了 %s。"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> attacks %s powerfully"
msgstr "<npcname> 強力地攻擊了 %s"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
msgid "Whirlwind Feet"
msgstr "旋風腳"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You whirlwind kick %s."
msgstr "你施展旋風踢擊中了 %s。"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "<npcname> whirlwind kicks %s."
msgstr "<npcname> 施展旋風踢擊中了 %s。"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
msgid "Iron Mine"
msgstr "鐵礦山"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
msgid "You blow away %s with Iron Mine."
msgstr "你用鐵礦山擊飛了 %s。"

#: .\nec_techniques.json
#, c-format
